	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_DECLAREWAR_1">
			<Text>You’ve been an annoyance for too long. It’s time you disappeared.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>You’ve beaten me this time. It’s time I went home anyway, treat your world well, you are nothing without it after all.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>So, another one has risen to shape the fate of this world. I am Jacqli, most powerful of all Reyvateil, don’t interfere with me and we might just get along.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>I am in politics because of the conflict between good and evil, and I believe that in the end good will triumph.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>If you want something said, ask a man; if you want something done, ask a woman.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>If you want to cut your own throat, don't come to me for a bandage.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_THATCHER_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING">
			<Text>Do not think me a fool; I see what you are doing with all those units near my borders. Remove them immediately or I will have to assume the worst of you.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_THATCHER_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING">
			<Text>I have precious little lands and resources as it is, I don’t appreciate your settling in lands that I consider mine. I suggest you re-think doing so in the future.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE">
			<Text>Our world is limited enough without borders holding us back. Free passage between our lands will benefit us both.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_THATCHER_LOSEWAR_1">
			<Text>You may have to fight a battle more than once to win it.</Text>
		</Row>
